A cyberpunk scene showing a person standing in a cluttered kitchen, their field of vision overwhelmed by countless floating holographic panels, glowing product recommendations, navigation arrows, and pulsing data streams in neon pink, electric blue, and acid green. The person's face is barely visible behind layers of translucent digital overlays, their expression caught between wonder and anxiety. The mundane domestic space—sink, refrigerator, countertops—is transformed into a chaotic digital jungle where every surface projects information. Reflections of the holograms shimmer on chrome appliances. The atmosphere is simultaneously dazzling and suffocating, with sharp geometric shapes competing for attention in the air. Rain-slicked window in the background reveals a dense urban nightscape filled with more floating advertisements. The color palette emphasizes harsh contrasts between warm indoor lighting and cold digital interference.
